2025-12-08  Michał Krzywkowski  <k.michal@zoho.com>

	Version 0.2.0

	- Minimum Emacs version was bumped to 28.

	- Fixed an issue with the parsing of process output caused by a
	change in one of the newer Emacs versions.

	- New command `flymake-x-debug' helps with defining new checkers
	by running a checker once and displaying retrieved information.

